Summary of "Raspberry Pi and MaKey MaKey Power Bus Stop Pac-Man"
---------------------------------------------------------------
by [Erdy Suryadarma](http://erdry.com) / 18111013.

This project made by [Trondheim Makers](http://trondheimmakers.com/) is about an *advertising campaign*, Raspberry Pi and MaKey MaKey-equipped bus stop ad that lets pedestrians play Pac-Man. 

**System Spesification:**
 1. Raspberry Pi running [RetroPie](http://blog.petrockblock.com/retropie/) and a (somewhat modified) [Makey Makey](http://www.makeymakey.com/).
 2. WS2812B led strip  
 3. Salvaged 17″ LCD with VGA input.  
 4. HDMI->VGA converter.  
 5. Wooden plate cut as the base

